txt.en: 'We can have many defenders standing in the towers and behind the walls of Hytbold, and a smithy set up to craft the finest of weapons, but if we do not have an armoury to store and keep the weapons, shields, and armour primed and ready for battle then it does not matter how many defenders we have. We must get the armoury rebuilt and ready to store our equipment.'
'Hytbold is one step closer to being rebuilt and restored.'
There is much work to do to rebuild the town of Hytbold.
There is much work to do to rebuild the town of Hytbold.
Bring the Tokens of Hytbold to Edgal
